<p>Surprised at CD’s account of <hi rend="italic">Bryanthus</hi>.</p>  
<p>H. Crüger’s approach to <hi rend="italic">Gongora</hi> fertilisation is beset with difficulties.</p>  
<p>Reports his work on self-sterility of <hi rend="italic">Oncidium</hi>.</p> 
